sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant System
    participant PINService

    User->>System: Request login
    System->>User: Prompt for password
    User->>System: Enter password
    System->>User: Validate password
    alt Password valid
        System->>User: Prompt for optional PIN
        User->>System: Choose to use PIN
        System->>PINService: Request PIN verification
        PINService->>User: Send PIN request
        User->>PINService: Enter PIN
        PINService->>System: Validate PIN
        System->>User: Access granted
    else Password valid, but no PIN
        System->>User: Access granted
    else Password invalid
        System->>User: Access denied
    end